dct_title_s: Erets Yiśraʾel : bi-yeme ha-Bayit ha-sheni, ha-Mishnah, ṿeha-Talmud (333 lif. s. ha-N. ʻad 640 li-s. ha-N.)
dct_description_sm: "Ṭevet 725, Detsember 1964." Later printings were published under the department's new name: Agaf ha-medidot. Relief shown by contours, shading and hachures. Includes inset of Negev Desert.
